                     <interp inst="t18300916-236-off1202" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18300916-236-cd1203" type="crimeDate">11th of July</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18300916-236-off1202 t18300916-236-cd1203"></join>, 1 pair of trousers, value 8s.; 1 pair of boots, value 2s., and 1 pair of braces, value 6d.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t18300916-236-victim1943" type="victimName">
                     Jeremiah 
